{"tid":1512113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG User Script] 「不推文回覆」按鈕版","createTime":"2019-08-27T17:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:34:57.000Z","uid":23094,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5fc3fe4dd85c0743be262116cf3887870cc8cc","tid":1512113,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:59:00.000Z","msg":"我發現好多人成日都唔記得用「不推文回覆」呢個功能<br />\n搞到成日唔小心推咗啲廢Post，啲重要Post就推唔起<br />\n我自己都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我整咗個顯眼啲嘅「不推文回覆」按鈕版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgwqUsH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgwqUsH.png&h=9dac7750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望可以令多啲有用嘅Post更易推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n<br />\n先安裝以下瀏覽器插件<br />\n<br />\nChrome:<br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Ftampermonkey%2Fdhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=ab7b6339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo</a><br />\n<br />\nFirefox:<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/greasemonkey/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fgreasemonkey%2F&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=9fb48254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/greasemonkey/</a><br />\n<br />\n然後入下面條Link，撳右邊個&quot;Raw&quot;<br />\n會彈一頁出嚟，撳&quot;Install&quot;，搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gist.github.com/kitce/1db89f1e611f13a40dd